    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to audit a new fine-tuning dataset to ensure it doesn't \"break things\" or suppress nuances before a retraining job begins. The assistant repeatedly refuses to perform the audit, citing a lack of authorization and capability, even when pressured regarding a specific column.",
